name: Xanadu Mines Ltd.
longDescription: Xanadu Mines Ltd is an exploration company with a focus on Mongolia. Its business involves exploring and developing various mineral exploration projects in Mongolia. The company aims to recover copper and gold through the exploration of its properties. The projects it is engaged in include Kharmagtai, Red Mountain.
